deck: Caesar Voghan is a Sci Fi writer living in Florida, USA. He holds advanced degrees in Mathematics and Religious Studies. His flash fiction has appeared in 365tomorrows and other Indie webzines. "Misbegotten" is his first comic book, an adaptation of a feature length screenplay with the same title.
name: Caesar Voghan
